{"tid":2362990,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"據推測，IZ * ONE的一些成員準備與CJ ENM延長合同","createTime":"2021-01-12T01:01:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-14T09:14:44.000Z","uid":205928,"like":8,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"6afb9535c242c5a7a5c5450f943e992d6c91c32b","tid":2362990,"uid":205928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T01:01:57.000Z","msg":"根據1月12日的一份媒體報導，CJ ENM與IZ * ONE成員各自機構之間的討論將在2021年開始。<br />\n<br />\n一位業內人士稱，CJ ENM最近會見了一些成員機構的代表，以討論有關IZ * ONE合同可能延期的細節。儘管報告指出，但並非每個IZ * ONE成員都如此。但就某些成員及其代理而言，他們早在去年10月就與CJ ENM進行了討論。 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oV037u3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoV037u3.jpg&h=b86037f7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tqity95.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftqity95.jpg&h=7ffcdfad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n此外，另一位業內人士也發表了這樣的聲明：&ldquo;儘管紙面上，IZ * ONE的合同於4月結束，但內部達成了旨在於2020年底結束該集團促銷活動的和解協議。生存計劃的首席人員已被逮捕並正在審判中，IZ * ONE成員共享的宿舍合同也於2020年12月終止。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n據推測，CJ ENM將尊重那些決定不延長與IZ * ONE的合同的機構的決定，同時與更支持該想法的機構合作。如果IZ * ONE成功地將其合同延長到2021年下半年，該小組將成為實現這一壯舉的第一個&ldquo;PRODUCE&rdquo;項目小組"},{"pid":"f32366c66d164f6bb7e88b689c68c291b6aa90e7","tid":2362990,"uid":205928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T01:02:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://m.isplus.joins.com/news/article/article.aspx?total_id=23968362#_enliple\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.isplus.joins.com%2Fnews%2Farticle%2Farticle.aspx%3Ftotal_id%3D23968362%23_enliple&d=bDhD0m8o4fsrNJ%2BdslRS%2BdMQoCHxbgs64DeXVNsql00%3D&h=03c3bf03\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.isplus.joins.com/news/article/article.aspx?total_id=23968362#_enliple</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.allkpop.com/article/2021/01/some-members-of-izone-supposedly-preparing-to-extend-promotion-contract-with-cj-enm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.allkpop.com%2Farticle%2F2021%2F01%2Fsome-mem